### Octopus Cosy Analyser API Requests
### Base URL - adjust port as needed when app is running
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@accountNumber = YOUR_ACCOUNT_NUMBER
@deviceId = YOUR_DEVICE_ID

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Sample Weather Forecast
GET {{baseUrl}}/weatherforecast

###

### 1. Setup Heat Pump Device
# Replace YOUR_ACCOUNT_NUMBER with your actual Octopus Energy account number
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/setup?accountNumber={{accountNumber}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Get Live Telemetry
# Replace YOUR_DEVICE_ID with the deviceId returned from setup
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/telemetry/{{deviceId}}

###

### 3. Sync Historical Data (Last 7 Days - Default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/sync/{{deviceId}}

###

### 4. Sync Historical Data (Custom Date Range)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/sync/{{deviceId}}?from=2024-02-05T00:00:00Z&to=2024-02-12T00:00:00Z

###

### 5. Get Consumption Data (Last 7 Days - Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/consumption/{{deviceId}}

###

### 6. Get Consumption Data (Custom Date Range)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/consumption/{{deviceId}}?from=2024-02-05T00:00:00Z&to=2024-02-12T00:00:00Z

###

### 7. List All Devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/devices

###

### Example Full Workflow:
### Step 1: Setup device (run once)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/setup?accountNumber=A-12345678

### Step 2: Copy deviceId from response, then sync data
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/sync/abc-123-def-456

### Step 3: View consumption data
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/heatpump/consumption/abc-123-def-456

###
